---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-tag">RAINFOREST MIND SOFTWARE</p>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">一个 INFP 程序员的小宇宙</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">用 AI 加持，做关注成长与连结的产品</p>
    <div class="hero-badge">✦ Vibe Coding · Solo Founder · 独立开发</div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: #2d3a1e;
    background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #4a5e35 0%, #2d3a1e 70%);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #8fa876;
    font-variant: small-caps;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    color: #f0ede8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: normal;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #a8b89a;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid #4a5e35;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    color: #8fa876;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
</style>
